highlights.text: “Lose My Mind (feat. Doja Cat) [From F1® The Movie]” by Don Toliver, Doja Cat, and F1 The Album has been on Viral Songs Taiwan the longest, at 74 days straight.
Delaney Jane has the most spots on Viral Songs Taiwan. “Bad Habits” is the highest at #10.
“熄灭” by TC is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Taiwan at #13.
“YKWTD” by Flowstrong, Dac, wannasleep, Gummy B, TroutFresh, Kumachan, 馬克SAVAGE.M, YoungLee, JAYRoll, FRαNKIE阿法, and That's My Shhh is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Taiwan, up 20 spots at #77.
